name: Trap-Jaw Hercules Beetle
text:
2+ Insect monsters with different names
Must first be Special Summoned (from your Extra Deck) by banishing the above cards from your GY. (You do not use "Polymerization".) You can only Special Summon "Trap-Jaw Hercules Beetle" once per turn this way. This card gains effects based on the number of materials with different card types (Ritual, Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, Pendulum, Link) used for its Fusion Summon.●2+: This card gains 1000 ATK.●3+: Once per turn: You can target 1 card on the field; return that target to the hand.●4+: You can activate this card's effect as a Quick Effect.
